     C* D15: per-field conditioning. Indicator 10 is never set,
     C* so a field gated by N10 (always-on via negation) prints,
     C* while a field gated by 10 (off) is suppressed.
     FPFDATA  IP  F    80              DISK
     FPFOUT   O   F    132             PRINTER
     IPFDATA      AA
     I                                     1   1   0DUMMY
     OPFOUT   D  1
     O                N10              10   'YES'
     O                10               20   'NO'
